subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Marshall Henderson missed 12 of his first 13 field-goal attempts but kept shooting, helping Mississippi upset Wisconsin in the N.C.A.A. tournament’s Round of 64.
